ZH: 请把墙上的灰尘用刷子刷掉。
EN: Please use a brush to remove the dust on the wall.

ZH: 这个刷子已经用了好多年了。
EN: This brush has been used for many years.

ZH: 我用刷子给车漆刷了一层。
EN: I used a brush to apply a coat of paint to the car.

ZH: 桌子上有一个刷子，你可以用它刷灰。
EN: There is a brush on the table, you can use it to dust.

ZH: 她用刷子梳理她的长发。
EN: She used a brush to comb her long hair.

ZH: 这个刷子太硬了，可以换一个吗？
EN: This brush is too hard, can I have a different one?

ZH: 孩子们正在用刷子刷颜料。
EN: The children are using brushes to paint.

ZH: 刷子的毛掉了一大块。
EN: A large chunk of the brush bristles fell out.

ZH: 我在商店里买了一组新的画笔和刷子。
EN: I bought a new set of paintbrushes and brushes at the store.

ZH: 刷子掉在地板上发出了响声。
EN: The brush fell on the floor and made a noise.

ZH: 请把这个刷子放回原位。
EN: Please put this brush back in its original place.

ZH: 我用这支刷子来刷我的畫作。
EN: I use this brush to paint my artwork.

ZH: 每次打扫房间我都用这支刷子来清理。
EN: I use this brush to clean the room every time.

ZH: 刷子的材质很重要。
EN: The material of the brush is very important.

ZH: 这支刷子的毛有点散了。
EN: The bristles of this brush are a little loose.

ZH: 我给她买了一套化妆刷子。
EN: I bought her a set of makeup brushes.

ZH: 这个刷子太软了，不适合我要做的工作。
EN: This brush is too soft, it is not suitable for the work I need to do.

ZH: 刷子的手柄很舒服。
EN: The handle of the brush is very comfortable.

ZH: 我正在用刷子清理花园里的树叶。
EN: I am using a brush to clear the leaves in the garden.

ZH: 这把刷子被用来刷灰。
EN: This brush is used for dusting.
